    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This car is in mint condition. The exterior is free of scratches, dents, or blemishes, with a clean and uniform finish. The interior shows no signs of wear, with all surfaces, upholstery, and trim in pristine shape. Mechanically, the car is in excellent working order with no known issues.",
